data.description: JULY/AUGUST MOVE IN! Strauss Luxury Package. To be built Strauss  interior unit in  Andale Green offers the only new townhomes in North Penn Schools, within walking distance to Pennbrook train station & across Stoney Creek Park. The Strauss is the largest home offered in Andale Green, with 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, and a 2-car garage. Here you'll find the space and customizing details of single-family living with the convenience of a townhome. On the main living level, a large kitchen with island opens onto a bright and airy living room and window-lined morning room, creating a perfect area for entertaining. The upper level boasts three bedrooms, two baths, and the laundry area. No need to worry about storage - each bedroom has generous closet space. The owner's  bedroom is a private retreat accented with a tray ceiling and featuring an large walk-in closet. The owner's bath boasts a soaking tub and separate shower with seat. On the lower level, the finished rec room is perfect for a home office, study space, or gym. You can even add an additional bedroom and bathroom for a comfortable guest suite. To be built homes with later deliveries available. All appliances included! White shaker-style hardwood cabinets with soft close drawers.  Other floor plans and home sites available. Photos are representative.
